    "course_title": "INTRODUCTION TO EDUCATIONAL LEADERSHIP",
    "description": "Examine leadership in K12 schools for more equitable outcomes. Delve into key social justice concepts, principal leadership, teacher leadership, the interplay between principals and informal/formal teacher leaders, and how a more robust, encompassing view of leadership can contribute to more equitable student learning outcomes.",
